snippet: Jane’s Walk tours, in honor of the urban critic Jane Jacobs, will take place across New York City this weekend, led by neighborhood residents.
abstract: Municipal Art Society of New York will offer several walking tours across New York City, led by neighborhood residents, to honor the life and work of urban critic Jane Jacobs.
lead_paragraph: Jane’s Walk tours, in honor of the urban critic Jane Jacobs, will take place across New York City this weekend, led by neighborhood residents.
